hcc_text: York Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Manhattan)
info: At York Avenue at East 60th Street and 60 St. Heliport Ramp, there were 2 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
